{"tid":1952069,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【係借出唔係政府徵用】警方借出八鄉少年警訊中心作檢疫","createTime":"2020-03-31T11:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T11:23:49.000Z","uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1d718455cc184308c585f4ad9c3c733724b86878","tid":1952069,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T11:15:34.000Z","msg":"警方表示，將借出八鄉少年警訊中心供政府用作檢疫用途。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，首階段改建工程已經完成，並於今日正式移交予衞生署，首階段包括 4座獨立檢疫中心，可提供88個單位。警方提到，次階段工程已經展開，將於操場上加建120間組合屋，預計於4月底完成後交予衞生署。檢疫中心將會由民安隊管理，警方會提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517974-20200331.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517974-20200331.htm&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhopBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=c244e2f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517974-20200331.htm&h=3026b492\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517974-20200331.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6aa997a4e05cb7ce39bd5d9b592efb1aec8da41a","tid":1952069,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T11:17:12.000Z","msg":"重要Post，唔該幫推啊！！<br />\n<br />\n【告急】呢一刻最逼切亦最有用嘅聯署<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fktGmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fktGmS</a>"},{"pid":"69f40751c872a9fe168d51c7e3cac49cadbbf451","tid":1952069,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:01:01.000Z","msg":"警方呼籲市民提供八鄉失蹤男子消息（附圖）<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  <img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202004/02/P2020040200374_photo_1172046.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202004%2F02%2FP2020040200374_photo_1172046.jpg&h=7e378dc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方今日（四月二日）呼籲市民提供一名在八鄉失蹤男子的消息。<br />\n<br />\n  二十歲男子林進榮於三月二十四日離開其位於石田路的住所後便告失蹤，其家人於三月二十八日向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n  他身高約一點七八米，體重約八十公斤，中等身材，尖面型，黃皮膚及蓄短黑髮。<br />\n<br />\n  任何人如有該失蹤男子的消息或曾見過他，請致電三六六一 三一一三或六二七三 五七八七或電郵至rmpu-ntn-1@police.gov.hk與新界北總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年4月2日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間13時48分"},{"pid":"80332a3f1c83e382fdae7c971c93888411cef633","tid":1952069,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:21:36.000Z","msg":"政府借予政府使用？"},{"pid":"105155a30f6860b91f4ed304a4397d5b520d2a1b","tid":1952069,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:23:49.000Z","msg":"警隊真係獨立於政府"}]}